Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\4c&HAE524C&}また明日ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}追寻着迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}流星  到达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:58.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}想知道的广阔世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:06.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}渴望实现  不要只是许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}打开窗
